<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>宝开12月活动</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico"> 
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{$path_img}/images/activity/2016_DecRedBow/activitytwomb/index.css?20161201">
  </head>
<body onload="querySignUp()">
<div class="content">
    <button class="btn btn-join" type="submit">立即参加</button>
    <button class="btn btn-joined" type="submit" style="display:none;" >您已参加</button>
    <button class="btn btn-overtime" type="submit" style="display:none;">活动结束</button>
    <div class="qrcode">
      <img src="{$path_img}/images/activity/2016_DecRedBow/activitytwomb/qrcode.jpg" alt="扫一扫下载手机版">
      <p>扫一扫下载手机版</p>
    </div>
    <p class="desc">活动期间每日19:00:00-22:59:59时段，用户在该时间内投注平台任意彩种，即可获得限时返利。</p>

    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table class="table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th><span>项目</span></th>
            <th colspan="7"><span>平台所有彩种</span></th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th><span>销量</span></th>
            <td>≧1,000</td>
            <td>≧5,000</td>
            <td>≧15,000</td>
            <td>≧35,000</td>
            <td>≧55,000</td>
            <td>≧150,000</td>
            <td>≧500,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="reward">
            <th><span>加奖奖金</span></th>
            <td>8元</td>
            <td>38元</td>
            <td>118元</td>
            <td>288元</td>
            <td>688元</td>
            <td>1,888元</td>
            <td>6,888元</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
	<div class="rules">
      <span class="title">活动细则</span>
      <ul class="rules-list">
        <li class="item">活动返奖，参与游戏只限于宝开彩票旗舰版及宝开彩票专业版平台所有彩票类游戏。投注必须为已开奖注单，视为有效投注，大乐博、PT与骰宝大小单双销量不计入活动销量内。</li>
        <li class="item">活动销量两个平台分别独立计算。</li>
        <li class="item">本次活动采取报名制，用户需要点击“立即报名”后才能获取活动奖金。注：VIP3（包含VIP3）以上用户无需报名即可参加。</li>
        <li class="item">超级2000玩法按实际投注额的80%进行结算。如：用户超级2000玩法中投注额为1,000，则结算销量为1,000*80%=800。</li>
        <li class="item">加奖奖金于次日18:00前派发。</li>
        <li class="item">活动期间禁止任何作弊行为，一经发现平台将取消参与活动资格，严重者将被冻结账号处理。</li>
        <li class="item">宝开平台保留活动最终解释权。</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
   <div class="footer"> ©2003-2016 宝开彩票 All Rights Reserved </div>
</body>
 <script src="{$path_js}/js/activity/2016_DecRedBow/week2/index.js"></script>
